headline: Allergan Aesthetics Announces Expansion of SKINVIVE by JUVÉDERM® into 35 New Markets, Reinforcing its Commitment to Advancing Global Skin Quality
summary: Allergan Aesthetics, an AbbVie company (NYSE: ABBV), today announced the roll-out of SKINVIVE by JUVÉDERM® in 35 additional markets this year bringing the total to 57 globally in 2025. This expansion underscores Allergan Aesthetics' global strategic commitment to enhancing skin quality worldwide.
